/.premium/court-orders-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum-back-in-to-schools/0000018f-0a2d-db42-a99f-afbf8fe20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，以色列没有提供证据证明近东救济工程处在加沙的工作人员属于恐怖组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</link><description>对该机构“中立性”的独立审查与对以色列声称 12 名工作人员参与 10 月 7 日袭击的调查是分开进行的</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-that-unrwa-staff-in-gaza-belong-to-terror-groups/0000018f-0866-d0d2-a7bf-7dffd6980000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹，以色列国防军拦截三架无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</link><description>以色列称在黎巴嫩袭击中打死两名真主党高级成员 ■ 《纽约时报》报道，以色列计划对伊朗发动更大规模的袭击，但被迫重新考虑 ■ 哈马斯称加沙医院发现数百具尸体 ■ 伊朗外长称欧盟制裁“令人遗憾” ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，以色列国防军在西岸开火造成一名巴勒斯坦人死亡，两人受伤 ■ 布林肯表示，哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击和以色列在加沙的反应引起了对人权的“深感不安”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article-live/un-says-israel-has-not-provided-proof-of-claims-that-unrwa-employees-belong-to-terror-orgs/0000018f-08b9-db42-a99f-adbfa0390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡家前举行逾越节家宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</link><description>逾越节前夕，数百人呼吁释放凯撒利亚的人质。一名亲戚向内塔尼亚胡呼喊，“在自由的节日里，有 133 名犹太公民被哈马斯囚禁，释放我们，这样我们就能有一位勇敢的领导人来达成协议”</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-23/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-hold-passover-seder-in-front-of-netanyahus-home/0000018f-06fd-d6a0-a9ef-c6fd1eb30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军情报主管因 10 月 7 日的失败而辞职，这对其他以色列国防领导人来说变成了沙漏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</link><description>阿哈龙·哈利瓦是哈马斯大屠杀后下台的最高级官员，他无法预测他继续担任以色列军队情报部门负责人会造成多么严重的内部危机，也无法预测他会成为右翼分子的目标极端分子</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/resignation-of-idf-intel-chief-over-oct-7-turns-hourglass-for-other-defense-leaders/0000018f-06a0-d682-afcf-16a7bdf10000</guid></item><item><title>美国不应该制裁一个流氓营，而应该关注内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</link><description>如果谴责极端正统的内扎·耶胡达以色列国防军营的“莱希法”涉及约旦河西岸的侵犯人权行为，那么以色列的整个政治梯队都需要承担责任。美国应该明确地说</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-sanctioning-a-rogue-battalion-the-u-s-should-focus-on-netanyahus-government/0000018f-0507-d6a0-a9ef-c59f68d90000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查发现，不到四分之一的以色列犹太人支持在加沙重建定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</link><description>以色列民主研究所进行的民意调查显示，多数以色列人认为应将加沙控制权交给国际部队，13%的人认为巴勒斯坦权力机构应承担责任</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/less-than-quarter-of-israeli-jews-in-favor-of-renewed-settlement-in-gaza-poll-finds/0000018f-0587-d64a-a9af-85efc6e30000</guid></item><it