ssover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</link><description>从“无战略的瘟疫”到“全面胜利的瘟疫”，自从六个多月前与哈马斯的战争开始以来，以色列领导人给他们的人民带来了一场又一场的瘟疫，而且还看不到结束的迹象</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/this-passover-remember-israels-10-self-inflicted-plagues-since-october-7/0000018f-00d0-d6a0-a9ef-c0dce9dd0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷发生汽车冲撞和枪击未遂事件，三人受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/three-people-lightly-wounded-in-car-ramming-attempted-shooting-in-jerusalem/0000018f-04cb-d6a0-a9ef-c4dfa95d0000</link><description>袭击者试图向行人开枪但失败后逃离现场，并在袭击现场附近的一家商店藏身时被捕</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/three-people-lightly-wounded-in-car-ramming-attempted-shooting-in-jerusalem/0000018f-04cb-d6a0-a9ef-c4dfa95d0000</guid></item><item><title>逾越节后，以色列面临选择：人质还是战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/after-passover-israel-will-have-to-choose-hostages-or-war/0000018f-0209-d6a0-a9ef-c29dc3490000</link><description>以色列目前的战略陷阱在各个方面都很明显：伊朗、黎巴嫩和加沙。 ■ 随着人质在囚禁中腐烂，政客们对其家人的求救声表现出冷漠甚至敌意。 ■ 以色列国防军高级军官会因为 10 月 7 日的失败而开始辞职吗？ ■ 拜登政府现在正瞄准内塔尼亚胡的核心弱点</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/after-passover-israel-will-have-to-choose-hostages-or-war/0000018f-0209-d6a0-a9ef-c29dc3490000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：内塔尼亚胡集团获得51个席位，甘茨留在战时联盟，领先优势缩小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-bloc-gets-51-seats-gantzs-lead-narrows-as-he-stays-in-wartime-coalition/0000018f-03a6-d224-a9cf-07f732b40000</link><description>该调查还探讨了这样一种情况：纳夫塔利·贝内特、摩萨德前局长约西·科恩和吉迪恩·萨尔联合成一个右翼名单，而前以色列国防军副局长亚尔·戈兰则领导工党和梅雷茨之间的左翼联盟</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/poll-netanyahu-bloc-gets-51-seats-gantzs-lead-narrows-as-he-stays-in-wartime-coalition/0000018f-03a6-d224-a9cf-07f732b40000</guid></item><item><title>真主党声称对以色列北部发射的火箭弹负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article-live/israel-hamas-war-day-199/0000018f-0383-d224-a9cf-07f3f43a0000</link><description>逾越节前夕，人质家属在内塔尼亚胡家门前举行“抗议家宴” ■ 以色列空军在向北部发射火箭弹后袭击黎巴嫩真主党目标 ■ 欧盟扩大对伊朗制裁 ■ 以色列国防军情报局长于 10 月 7 日辞职 ■ 国防部长加兰特在有报道称美国打算制裁极端正统派营后，支持该营 ■ 两名嫌疑人因耶路撒冷汽车撞击袭击事件被捕，造成三人轻伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:16:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article-live/israel-hamas-war-day-199/0000018f-0383-d224-a9cf-07f3f43a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员不会因涉嫌袭击被拘留的贝都因人而面临指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-lawmaker-wont-face-charges-on-alleged-assault-on-detained-bedouins/0000018f-0278-db32-a58f-feff0e4b0000</link><description>来自本-格维尔党的议会议员阿尔蒙·科恩 (Almong Cohen) 在 1 月份就 2013 年发生的一起事件接受质询，据称，当时约有 12 名警察殴打了三名以色列贝都因嫌疑人。检方以无罪为由下令结案。科恩：“我不会为任何事情道歉”</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 21:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-22/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-lawmaker-wont-face-charges-on-alleged-assault-on-detained-bedouins/0000018f-0278-db32-a58f-feff0e4b0000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易谈判处于危机模式，以色列希望利雅得能够提供帮助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-talks-are-in-crisis-mode-and-israel-is-hoping-that-riyadh-can-help/0000018f-0219-d64a-a9af-86fb25350000</link><description>以色列战时内阁继续寻求解决与哈马斯谈判僵局的方案 ■ 与沙特阿拉伯达成协议可能会达成释放人质的协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-talks-are-in-crisis-mode-and-israel-is-hoping-that-riyadh-can-help/0000018f-0219-d64a-a9af-86fb25350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长批准政府就正统派法律草案聘请独立顾问的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-approves-govt-request-for-independent-counsel-on-haredi-draft-law/0000018f-01dc-d64a-a9af-85ffa1aa0000</link><description>总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫·米亚拉 (Gali Baharav-Miara) 表示，她无法在法庭上捍卫政府的立场，即极端正统派以色列人应免除以色列国防军服役</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-approves-govt-request-for-independent-counsel-on-haredi-draft-law/0000018f-01dc-d64a-a9af-85ffa1aa0000</guid></item></channel></rss>